lead_paragraph: After an offseason cluttered by contract negotiations and surgery, Rickard Rakell returned to the Anaheim Ducks' lineup just in time for a rivalry game.

headline.print_headline: Rakell Returns to Lead Anaheim Ducks' 4-0 Rout of LA Kings
